bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "parachutedrop-rust-server"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "parachutedrop-rust-server"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true

[dependencies]
actix-web = "4"
base64 = "0.21.0"
cosmos-sdk-proto = "0.16.0"
env_logger = "0.10"
json = "*"
jsonrpc-core-client = "18.0.0"
prost = "0.11.5"
protobuf = "3.2.0"
serde_json = "1.0"
strum = "0.24.1"
strum_macros = "0.24.3"
tonic = "0.8.3"
web3 = "0.18.0"

[dependencies.ibc-proto]
git = "https://github.com/cosmos/ibc-proto-rs"
branch = "main"

[dependencies.reqwest]
version = "0.11.13"
features = ["json", "native-tls-alpn"]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.23.0"
features = ["macros", "rt-multi-thread", "full"]

[dev-dependencies]
protobuf-codegen-pure = "2.14"

[build-dependencies]
tonic-build = "0.8.4"
